Version 2 changes

Reconfigured knife system on the race course. Fps issues fixed. Water doesn't kill in the Aztec stage anymore.

### Info Give feedback, rate and if you'd like vote as me the mapper of the month. Stages are randomly choosen every round. Headshot or normal mode is choosen randomly every round. ### - Knife areas - - Final destination - n64 Link castle - Kirby's dreamland - Battlefield - Pirate ship - Floating facility ### - Gun areas - - Rooftop - Aztec - Ice - Deagle - Metal stage ### - Specials - Obstacle course
